snippet: A day after blinking in a showdown on the range, federal land managers pledged to pursue efforts to resolve a conflict with a southern Nevada rancher who has refused to pay grazing fees for 20 years....

headline.print_headline: Feds to Pursue Effort to End Dispute With Rancher
headline.main: Feds to Pursue Effort to End Dispute With Rancher

lead_paragraph: A day after blinking in a showdown on the range, federal land managers pledged to pursue efforts to resolve a conflict with a southern Nevada rancher who has refused to pay grazing fees for 20 years.
